## ğŸ“ Related Project

> This repo supports the main project: [SecureFileTransfer](https://github.com/Poken-ninja/SecureFileTransfer)

It contains scripts that:

* Encrypt and decrypt files using AES (and later RSA)
* Work in batch mode for multiple files
* Include logging and backup features

---

## âš™ï¸ Basic Setup (Quick Glance)

> For full steps, read `setup_guide.md`

```bash
# 1. Clone the main repo
https://github.com/Poken-ninja/SecureFileTransfer.git
cd SecureFileTransfer

# 2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# 3. Activate venv
# Windows
.\venv\Scripts\activate
# macOS/Linux
source venv/bin/activate

# 4. Install required packages
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## ğŸ¤ Contribution Guidelines

* Always use the virtual environment
* Never commit `.pyc`, `venv/`, or `.idea/` folders
* Update `requirements.txt` if you add any new libraries:

  ```bash
  pip freeze > requirements.txt
  ```

